text = "You lie to the villagers and proclaim: \"Let God decide. We will use trial by ordeal.\""
success_text = "You declare a trial by water. The woman is bound and thrown into the river. To everyone's shock, she sinks like a stone, proving her innocence in the eyes of God and man. Your men pull her out, sputtering but alive. The peasants are humbled, and you are seen as both pious and wise for letting God reveal the truth."
failure_text = "You declare a trial by water. The woman is bound and thrown into the river. Horrifyingly, her simple wool dress traps enough air to make her float for a few moments - \"proof\" of her guilt. The mob, their fears confirmed, drag her from the water and carry out their own justice before your guards can intervene. Your attempt at a clever solution has backfired into brutal chaos."
